parameters: "XIN-AMON"
You collapse in exhaustion as the last head of the newborn
rodent god is decapitated.
endcut/X1
But your triumph dissipates as the rodent continues thrashing,
unaffected by your attacks.
The monster had been growing this whole time...
You thought you were doing well, but now realize you've been
fighting an increasingly insignificant part of a now much more
massive creature.
Worse still, it seems to be growing faster now that you've cut
off its heads.
But there's nowhere to run. The infinitely expanding rodent
flesh surges towards you - around you.
A piece of your astronomer friends' minds held back the
abomination's growth to give you a fighting chance...
...but there is none now. There is no thought or soul in the beast.
It only grows and eats.
endcut/X2
Even the nearby buildings are covered in the god's flesh. Its
expansion is exponential.
The pleading sobs and horrified shrieks below are cut short by
thrashing limbs and snapping jaws.
A great tower of rodent limbs rises in the distance. It must be
a hundred meters away. Another erupts from the carnage behind
you.
The rodent mass closes in on you. There's nowhere left to go.
endcut/X3
A tendril of flesh and fur and beady eyes wraps around your
arm. It's too tight - you can't pull away. Sharp incisors rip into
your ankle.
endcut/X4
Bulbous tumors grow on your shoulder. The flesh bursts,
revealing beady rodent eyes beneath. They spread to your arm.
Your own hand bites your face.\.\.\.\. You can taste it.\.\.\.\.
\C[10]It tastes like...\.\.\.\.\^
\..\..\..you feel a renewed urge to gnaw on something, but there
is nothing to gnaw.
There was a lot to gnaw on before, but there is nothing now.
endcut/X5a
endcut/X5b
endcut/X5c
There was the Moon, but, despite the half-remembered stories,
it was only a rock. So you let it go.\.\. For now.
There is only the cold void of space.
There was a lot of screaming before, for a long time, but it's
all over now.
You almost miss it.
You miss\..\..\..\C[5] them.
You\. feel\. a\. little\. bit\. \C[14]lonely.\.\.\.\.\^
setAchievement("Ending_Xinamon");
